externally and internally my type.

25
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:34,763
Half of me is excited,
and half of me is scared.

26
00:01:35,290 --> 00:01:38,458
There will be a bunch of strangers,
so I wonder what I'll have to say.

27
00:01:39,255 --> 00:01:41,221
Aside from everything
else, I hope I can get

28
