Did you see a ghost?

72
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:47,397
- It's my first time.
- I see. That's fine.

73
00:03:47,422 --> 00:03:50,337
If you have any questions,
you can ask Do-yeon.

74
00:03:58,687 --> 00:04:02,260
(TVING Original: Love Catcher in Seoul)

75
00:04:02,888 --> 00:04:06,783
'Charming men and women who
came to "Love Catcher" find true love.'

76
00:04:07,631 --> 00:04:09,791
However, among these
"Love Catchers," there are

77
00:04:09,887 --> 00:04:12,327
