And if two Money Catchers become a couple,
they'll lose both love and the prize.

82
00:04:29,838 --> 00:04:33,461
Will they be able to find
true love among the lies?

83
00:04:34,068 --> 00:04:40,349
"Love Catcher in Seoul," a psychological
romance in a beautiful city, starts now!

84
00:04:42,523 --> 00:04:45,157
