I really like dating programs. I love them.

87
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,653
- You do?
- Yes, like "Transferring Love"?

88
00:04:55,081 --> 00:04:57,432
- That was really fun.
- Yes, I saw that.

89
00:04:57,457 --> 00:04:59,975
Of course, I saw the first and
second "Love Catcher," too.

90
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,048
There are so many amazing twists.

91
00:05:02,073 --> 00:05:03,305
At the end when he...

92
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:05,670
When Chan-woo smiled.

93
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:08,173
- We felt the same way.
- It's really famous.

94
00:05:08,383 --> 00:05:13,001
I know it's just a show, but I
remember being really immersed in it.

95
00:05:13,563 --> 00:05:16,356
I think it's going to be
really interesting because

96
00:05:16,558 --> 00:05:21,471
