Hello.

236
00:15:18,225 --> 00:15:19,225
Hi.

237
00:15:21,141 --> 00:15:23,514
- Hello.
- Hello.

238
00:15:23,539 --> 00:15:25,906
(He enters the bar with a strong aura.)

239
